    ¬∑ -- If there exists `Œ¥ ‚àà (0, Œµ)`, then we choose `Œ¥`-nhd of `a` and `(Œµ-Œ¥)`-nhd of `b`
      filter_upwards [(eventually_abs_sub_lt a Œ¥0).prod_nhds
